    "description": "《向邪恶进军》 是一款诡异向 2.5D 银河恶魔城风格的探索游戏，其故事发生在奇异的涔溪（Rainybrook）小镇，该镇如今被一个名为“邪恶”的神秘团伙所统治。<br>吸收“邪恶”的力量，在曾经是家园的险地中奋战，在为时已晚之前找到失散的朋友艾拉！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动作游戏</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153750/extras/d1404192b3a2eee05ad8322237552bb1.poster.avif?t=1716384118\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153750/extras/d1404192b3a2eee05ad8322237552bb1.webm?t=1716384118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153750/extras/d1404192b3a2eee05ad8322237552bb1.mp4?t=1716384118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在这个精心打造的 2.5D 世界中，你需要一边跳跃、摇摆，与危险的敌人搏斗，一边解决各种谜题和探寻秘密。解锁新的技能，战胜邪恶者的怪兽--即使在此过程中你会逐渐失去人性。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>奇事异人</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153750/extras/8884bfa6e22771c6c8a50e0f2f8645ee.poster.avif?t=1716384118\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153750/extras/8884bfa6e22771c6c8a50e0f2f8645ee.webm?t=1716384118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153750/extras/8884bfa6e22771c6c8a50e0f2f8645ee.mp4?t=1716384118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>海滨小镇涔溪（Rainybrook） 古色古香，但已被邪恶者的怪兽侵占，来此探索，你将认识善良而有特色的镇民，帮助他们完成各种任务，了解他们的故事，并发现可能的线索来找到你失散的朋友艾拉。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动态交互式世界</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153750/extras/2ea1bfe3146bd348d8372a597e616189.poster.avif?t=1716384118\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153750/extras/2ea1bfe3146bd348d8372a597e616189.webm?t=1716384118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153750/extras/2ea1bfe3146bd348d8372a597e616189.mp4?t=1716384118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> 体验互动世界，感受日夜交替和天气变化对游戏的不同影响。在夜晚遇到不同的怪物！寻找只有在特定条件下才会出现的物品和支线任务！",
